===Pronunciation===
* {{audio|en-us-trillion.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|ɪljən}}

===Cardinal number===
'''trillion'''

# (''US; modern British & Australian, [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]]'') A [[million]] [[million]]: 1 followed by twelve zeros, 10<sup>12</sup>.
# (''dated British & Australian, [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]]'') A [[million]] [[million]] [[million]]: 1 followed by eighteen zeros, 10<sup>18</sup>.

* ''Western (Arabic) Numeral'' '''trillion''', '''10<sup>12</sup>''' [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]], '''10<sup>18</sup>''' [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]]
** '''Previous''': [[billion]]: [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]] 10<sup>9</sup>, [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]] 10<sup>12</sup>
** '''Next''': [[quadrillion]]: [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]] 10<sup>15</sup>, [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]] 10<sup>24</sup>
* ISO prefix: [[tera-]]

